{"tid":442504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國民黨：與中共有默契 在對方面前不提中華民國","createTime":"2017-10-20T16:21:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T17:03:29.000Z","uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"28fafc5704b45eea6dea8adf9dc628455992abc6","tid":442504,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T16:21:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20171019/1225127/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20171019%2F1225127%2F&d=HvnfUf5OLwwsvTyJ8D7oaV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=b02051c0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20171019/1225127/</a><br />\n<br />\n中國共產黨昨舉行第19次全國代表大會揭幕，國民黨昨致賀電給中共中央，網友及立委質疑全文未有「中華民國」，國民黨發言人洪孟楷列出歷屆的賀電且回應，用西元年是雙方的「相互默契」。<br />\n「國慶日喊得震天價響，碰到對岸又龜縮起來，中華民國被國民黨消滅了？」時代力量立委徐永明在臉書表示，國民黨召開全代會，對岸不讀不回，未收到中共的賀電，對岸召開19大，國民黨仍獻殷勤，寫了封賀電給予祝賀。寫給老共的信卻不見「中華民國」，「難道『中華民國』對國民黨而言那麼丟臉嗎？」網友在《批踢踢實業坊》也熱議該話題。<br />\n部分網友認為，一般正式的公文、文件或獎狀，會寫「中華民國XXX年」，該賀電既然寫出「106」年，括號內為西元年，但106前面又沒有「中華民國」，認為刻意去掉該字樣。<br />\n國民黨文傳會副主委、該黨發言人洪孟楷在臉書上貼出過往從馬英九、洪秀柱到現任吳敦義主席的賀電，對日期書寫方式均一致，「中共方面回覆是用西元紀年，並不會稱中華人民共和國，這是相互默契，也就是具體的一中各表」，認為這樣才是「真正兩岸能夠務實穩定發展的基石」。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"d6669a75ab6850c9ee4b486a67ad828ae90a722b","tid":442504,"uid":37218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T16:23:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好激嬲中共"},{"pid":"d7250f629b21fb6c6b3384ad9e5b760df9e4c9c4","tid":442504,"uid":8810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T16:36:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好激嬲中共</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afad0a16ca1bc1c6f40647a5bad4be3821693165","tid":442504,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T16:43:25.000Z","msg":"其實而家KMT咩定位，完全戲都唔做全力賣台，仲會有人投佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4e0652b4410a7401b7e5a7e461aedabcfcbb32","tid":442504,"uid":24730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T16:56:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實而家KMT咩定位，完全戲都唔做全力賣台，仲會有人投佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪同香港民主黨差唔多，啲人都會照投"},{"pid":"72625db553db0b2e310c1c3f84d69eb77fe486e8","tid":442504,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T17:03:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}